Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.25,0:09:22.74,Ai_CH,,0,0,0,,已知sinθ+cosθ=1/2…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.35,Kasumi_CH,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.55,Ai_CH,,0,0,0,,sin指的是…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.39,Karin_CH,,0,0,0,,这个角度是…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.89,Ai_CH,,0,0,0,,函数是这样的…
