Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.16,Ai_CH,,0,0,0,,对对 就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.92,Yu_CH,,0,0,0,,解出来了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.10,Karin_CH,,0,0,0,,还是不行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.94,Kasumi_CH,,0,0,0,,已被榨干
