Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.46,Rina_CH,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.08,Rina_CH,,0,0,0,,如果是抽签
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.32,0:10:33.46,Rina_CH,,0,0,0,,那就没什么可说的 概率是1/12
